Destroy specific resource command --------> terraform destroy -target resourcename.usergivenresourcename 

install provider plugin -------> terraform init

view the plan -------> terraform plan

create infra -----> terraform apply

comments part in terraform code ----> /*     comments go here */

to see state file and view -----> terraform show

use varibale explicit ------> terraform plan -var="instacetype=t2.micro"

varibles.tf -----> to mention  all variable in a file 

terraform.tfvars---> store all common variables used in variables.tf

set veriable in window and linxu to use default values --->  
                
                setx TF_VAR_variablename
                 
                setx TF_VAR_instancetype t2.micro
                
                
print the set variable -------> 
  
            echp %TF_VAR_instancetype%
            
   output ----> t2.micro


varible "varibalename" 
{
type = string
}

varibale type : List,string, Map {name="viraj", cell=122445646}
